legend: 2009, Poland.  Gold medal match of the FIVB Beach Volleyball World Tour in Stare Jablonki, Poland. Gold with Pedro Solberg.

2008, Sanya, China, FIVB Beach VolleyBall World Tour, gold medal match, closing out the 2008 season with a final win over Roberto Pitta and Pedro Cunha, Harley Marques with Benjamin Insfran gets his 7th win 21-17, 21-19, ranking number one. (Universal Sports, UniversalSports.com)

2010, The Hague, Netherlands, FIVB Mens World Tour Beach Volleyball, Casey Jennings and Kevin Wong (USA) win two long rallies again Benjamin Insfran and Bruno Oscar Schmidt (BRA) in crazy rain and wind.

2010, The Hague, Netherlands, FIVB Mens World Tour Beach Volleyball, Casey Jennings and Kevin Wong (USA), the first lucky loser to be in the final beat Benjamin Insfran and Bruno Oscar Schmidt (BRA), 21-18, 18-21, 17-15
